Explination of Implementation

key:	32	16	8	4	2	1
 W : 	 0	 1	0	1	1	1

Pointer Finger: 1
Middle Finger: 2
Ring Finger: 4
Pinky: 8
Thumb: 16
Thumb: 32

This Chorded Keyboard design uses basic binary principles, along with different modes to keep the number or required keys low, but possible cominations high

Mode 1: Alpha

